metadata.title: Sitka Back-Tailed Deer SurveyI - PWS

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest, Cordova Ranger District in cooperation with Alaska Department of Fish

metadata.description: Data Type: Mammals;   This data set is taken from Prince William Sound transects to monitor Sitka Black-tailed deer populations using pellet-group survey methods. Transects were grouped by the geographic areas of Hawkins Island, Hinchinbrook Island, Montague Island and Western Prince William Sound.
